# Feature development — architecture map (Seismo 0.5)

This rule is the **routing table** for future work. It does not replace the specialist rules; it tells you **which constraints apply** and **where to put code**. When in doubt, read the linked rule file in `.cursor/rules/`.

## Specialist rules (read the relevant one before coding)

| Topic | Rule file |
|-------|-----------|
| Core vs plugin, repos, UTC, bounded queries, retention, plugin_run_log | `core-plugin-architecture.mdc` |
| Session auth (dormant), CSRF, public whitelist | `auth-dormant-by-default.mdc` |
